1)Which of the following when added to content attribute of meta tag will set the initial zoom level for a page?
--> initial-scale=1.0

2)Why do we need Media Query?
--> Perticularly to style elements depending upon the browser size

3)Which of the following media types can be used in defining a media query?
--> all, print, screen, speech

4)Which of the following will optimize the size of the page according to the device size?
--> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

5)What could be the possible values of the width property of content attribute in meta tag ?
--> 500, device-width

6)Which of the following media features can be used in defining a media query?
--> min-width, max-height, orientation

